      "writtenOn": "2018-12-11T13:09:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would add a comment: \"As a reminder, the time-based folder is just to help the humans look up data after the fact and prevent duplication of filename. If the time isn\u0027t exact or out of sync with other machines, that will not impede Gold\u0027s ingestion.\"",
